font-family:FangSong;mso-bidi-font-family:SimSun'>测试</span><span
style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:FangSong;mso-bidi-font-family:SimSun'>[1]<span
lang=ZH-CN>。学术圈至今对该思想实验的讨论还在继续，但是我觉得这个思想实验更容易让我们认识到语言的意义</span>(meaning)<span
lang=ZH-CN>和语言的形式</span>(form)<span lang=ZH-CN>的区别。</span>[1]<span lang=ZH-CN>的作者</span><span
class=SpellE>Bender&amp;Koller</span><span lang=ZH-CN>提出了一个思想实验</span>---<span
lang=ZH-CN>章鱼测试：两个人</span> A <span lang=ZH-CN>和</span> B <span lang=ZH-CN>独自生活在偏远的岛屿上，但通过跨洋电缆用英语短信与对方交流。一只超级智能的章鱼</span></span><span
style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Apple Color Emoji";mso-ascii-font-family:
FangSong;mso-fareast-font-family:FangSong;mso-hansi-font-family:FangSong;
mso-bidi-font-family:SimSun;mso-char-type:symbol-ext;mso-symbol-font-family:
"Apple Color Emoji"'>&#128025;</span><span lang=ZH-CN style='font-size:11.0pt;
font-family:FangSong;mso-bidi-font-family:SimSun'>坐在海底，虽无法到达也无法观察两个岛屿，却可以轻敲电缆并在任意长的时间段内窃听</span><span
style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:FangSong;mso-bidi-font-family:SimSun'>A <span
lang=ZH-CN>和</span> B<span lang=ZH-CN>的谈话。最终，</span></span><span
style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Apple Color Emoji";mso-ascii-font-family:
FangSong;mso-fareast-font-family:FangSong;mso-hansi-font-family:FangSong;
mso-bidi-font-family:SimSun;mso-char-type:symbol-ext;mso-symbol-font-family:
"Apple Color Emoji"'>&#128025;</span><span lang=ZH-CN style='font-size:11.0pt;
font-family:FangSong;mso-bidi-font-family:SimSun'>感到孤独，决定插手谈话，掐断</span><span
style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:FangSong;mso-bidi-font-family:SimSun'>B<span
lang=ZH-CN>的通讯并冒充其对</span>A<span lang=ZH-CN>进行回复。问题是</span></span><span
style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Apple Color Emoji";mso-ascii-font-family:
FangSong;mso-fareast-font-family:FangSong;mso-hansi-font-family:FangSong;
mso-bidi-font-family:SimSun;mso-char-type:symbol-ext;mso-symbol-font-family:
"Apple Color Emoji"'>&#128025;</span><span lang=ZH-CN style='font-size:11.0pt;
