SimSun'>通过测试的想法。</span><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:FangSong;
mso-bidi-font-family:SimSun'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p><span lang=ZH-CN style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:FangSong;mso-bidi-font-family:
SimSun'>比如，假设</span><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:FangSong;
mso-bidi-font-family:SimSun'> A <span lang=ZH-CN>在岛上突然被一只愤怒的熊追赶，抓起几根棍子自卫，并向</span>
B <span lang=ZH-CN>征求意见。</span>A<span lang=ZH-CN>会问</span>B<span lang=ZH-CN>“</span>Help!
I<span lang=ZH-CN>’</span>m being chased by a bear! All I have is a stick! What
do I do?<span lang=ZH-CN>”这个时候，章鱼</span></span><span style='font-size:11.0pt;
